<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakavaruṣamulu 
<lb n="2"/>10<unclear>59</unclear>nēṁṭi Uttarāyanasaṁ 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>krāṁttinimittamunaṁddu veṁgi 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> yyaraḍḍikamu gala koṁḍapaḍmaṭi 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> raḍḍi tallidaṁḍrulaku dharmmārttha 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mugā gōniyapūṁḍi śrīsōmēśvara 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>mahādēvaraku guḍi Etticce yā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> muna tana kaṭṭiṁccina ceṟvuvenaka 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nu maṟturu sēnu dēvara nivēdyamu 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nakuṁ beṭṭe Idēvaraku Akhaṁḍava 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>rttidīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina goṟiya 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>lu 55 vīniṁ jēkoni kro <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kāma (The rest Is Illegible <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> )
</p>

